  "texts": [
    "The specificity of the automatic AI detection systems (89.23%) was above chance level.",
    "Recall and precision were null, as none of the detectors was able to correctly detect text generated by an AI.",
    "The F1 score could not be calculated, for the same reason.",
    "The ability of the systems to discriminate between AI and human texts was also analyzed using the area under the curve (AUC) (see Figure 7).",
    "The value of the AUC did not differ significantly from chance level (AUC = 0.446, p = 0.281)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}